						<summary>

						<p>Three faces of a broken slab kept in the same place [No. 211/A.R. No. 770].</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary record commences with the imprecatory verses and seems to refer to a gift of land the details of which are lost. It is in the characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

